com.tsgrp.migration.event.pipeline

Interface PipelineEventListener

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    AbstractPipelineEventListener, BasicPipelineEventListener
    Deprecated.

    @Deprecated
public interface PipelineEventListener
    This interface defines all events that can occur and are listened for in the pipeline. Most of these are stubbed out in AbstractPipelineEventListener.
